<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
    <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    <main class="container-fluid p-0">
     
      <div class="banner p-0 d-none d-lg-block">
        <a href="/blogs/4">
          <div class="banner-text">
            <h4 class="m-0">What is super-compensation?</h4>
            <span class="text-muted">Feb 12</span>
            <article class="banner-desc">
              The body is always seeking to maintain a state of equilibrium so it
              will constantly adapt to the stress from its environment. Training
              is simply the manipulation of the application of stress and the
              bodyâ€™s subsequent adaptation to that stress to maintain equilibrium.
            </article>
          </div>
        </a>
       
      </div>
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Recent</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="top-picks container">
        <% for(let i=1;i<=5;i++){ %>
        <a href="/blogs/<%= data[i].id %>">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="blog-cover col-5 col-sm-5 col-md-3">
              <img class="blog-cover-img" src="<%=data[i].image %>" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="blog-content col-7 col-sm-7 col-md-9">
              <p class="blog-title"><%=data[i].title%></p>
              <p class="date text-muted m-0"><%=data[i].date%></p>
              <span class="blog-description">
                <%= data[i].description %> 
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
  </body>
  <script
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  ></script>
</html>
